@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
title A UTXO in Bitcoin vs in Cardano

package "Bitcoin UTXO" {
  [Value\n(satoshis)] as BV
  [Locking script\nscriptPubKey] as BS
}
note bottom of BS
  Unlocked by scriptSig / witness.
  Script sees the unlocking data
  and signature checks; no attached
  state, no view of sibling outputs.
end note

package "Cardano eUTXO" {
  [Value\n(ADA + native assets)] as EV
  [Address\n(payment + staking credential)] as EA
  [Datum\nstate attached to the output] as ED
}
note bottom of ED
  At spend time the validator also
  receives a Redeemer (argument) and
  the Script Context (the whole tx).
end note

BV -[hidden]-> BS
EV -[hidden]-> EA
EA -[hidden]-> ED
BS ..> EV : Cardano extends\nthe same coin with
@enduml
